38787>>>>>>>        Else Begin
38788>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38789>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38790>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38791>>>>>>>        End
38791>>>>>>>>
38791>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
